    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several noticeable dents, rusted panels, and fading paint throughout. Mechanically, the car is currently unreliable; it has difficulty starting, the engine runs roughly, and the transmission slips during gear changes. The interior is also heavily worn with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it is priced accordingly for someone willing to invest the necessary time and repairs.",
