    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable surface scratches, some minor paint fading on the roof, and a small dent on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear on the upholstery and some scuffing on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require minor maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
