      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously maintained and showing no signs of wear, it represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a standard of care that is truly uncompromising. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that retains its original luster and mechanical integrity. We invite discerning buyers to experience this peerless example of engineering refinement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
